snippet.title: Chew Chew Mimic Playdate Trailer
snippet.description:
Our New Game Chew Chew Mimic will be comig to playdate and NES soon
Lowtek Games are working with John Riggs to bring this game to life.

John Riggs:
https://www.youtube.com/@JohnRiggs

This video was initaly shown as part of the tiny yellow machine playdate indie direct found here
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dU_6qfiDft4&ab_channel=TinyYellowMachine
